{"tid":467334,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"放蛇測明星食店　克勤阿倫大勝　林子善店員黑面","createTime":"2017-11-13T11:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T08:51:36.000Z","uid":79219,"like":7,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c611e4965aac4fcac496f9b912bc73bf9435919f","tid":467334,"uid":79219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3a-WDsfRZtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3a-WDsfRZtI&d=Wqqs1%2FQuREATe5Sljs4VV9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f10ee45c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3a-WDsfRZtI</a><br />\n總結：校長贏得有理<br />\n識飲識食的譚校長對食物要求高，員工態度好，講解詳細有耐性，整體水準偏高，故「左麟右李」贏得有理。「華星冰室」開業多年，其食物質素確令記者大跌眼鏡，無想過招牌菜黑松露炒蛋會完全無松露味，可幸店員的態度令店舖挽回不少分數，應記一功！至於「龍鳳冰室」雖然被店員態度及錯漏百出拉低分數，幸好子善已得悉此事，即火速承諾跟進改善，抵讚！"},{"pid":"5a36b8780a59820de9ebfa214c9a50b118057acc","tid":467334,"uid":79219,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家估下校長會唔會雞左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e7940c098bd22cacab9f6887e6ae43c9b48cec","tid":467334,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":152,"score":-140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b460d09fa7005545da6353b11af620e82c42022","tid":467334,"uid":25028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家估下校長會唔會雞左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會 大把人咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2c98e34761ce4a66680c96dba3f518b1f99d57","tid":467334,"uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"有無咁唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁倒瀉"},{"pid":"d79e8161f2e79a476f89aed3dc9ec2c42a06d